O 37002:2021 for guidelines on whistleblowing management system),<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="295dc3cd-8c06-4173-d2c2-047339340cdb"?></p><p><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="9276395" change-id="75f15599-1c7d-499f-fcf8-8daa067333b6" timestamp="1671534677054"?>—    a procedure to address the claims made.<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="75f15599-1c7d-499f-fcf8-8daa067333b6"?></p></sec>